c: 17
v: 73
t: "(Aey Muhammad), in logon ne is koshish mein koi kasar utha nahin rakkhi ke tumhein fitne mein daal kar us Wahee se pher dein jo humne tumhari taraf bheji hai, taa-ke tum hamare naam par apni taraf se koi baat ghado(fabricate). Agar tum aisa karte to woh zaroor tumhein apna dost bana letey"